{{作品名稱|name=''Life''|hk=捕捉占士甸|tw=叛逆年代|cn=生活}}是一部美國、德國、英國、加拿大和澳大利亞合拍的2015年[[傳記片|傳記]][[劇情片|劇情片]]，為[[安東·寇班|安東·寇班]]執導。電影根據於《[[生活_(雜誌)|生活]]》攝影師[[丹尼斯·史托克|丹尼斯·史托克]]和好萊塢男星[[詹姆斯·狄恩|詹姆斯·狄恩]]之間的友誼故事，兩人分別由[[羅伯·派汀森|羅伯·派汀森]]與[[丹恩·德翰|丹恩·德翰]]飾演<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson and Dane DeHaan to Star in ‘Life’|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-life-1200600368/|publisher=Variety|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2014-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113163459/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-life-1200600368/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Dane DeHaan to Play James Dean Alongside ‘Twilight’ Star Robert Pattinson in ‘Life’’|url=http://www.thewrap.com/dane-dehaan-to-play-james-dean-alongside-twilight-star-robert-pattinson-in-life/|publisher=The Wrap|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2014-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220061756/http://www.thewrap.com/dane-dehaan-to-play-james-dean-alongside-twilight-star-robert-pattinson-in-life/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Dane DeHaan and Robert Pattinson Get LIFE, Drea de Matteo Finds DARK PLACES, and Sophie Cookson to Lead THE SECRET SERVICE for Matthew Vaughn|url=http://collider.com/dane-dehaan-robert-pattinson-life/|publisher=Collider|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2014-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131090609/http://collider.com/dane-dehaan-robert-pattinson-life/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該片於2015年2月9日的[[第65屆柏林影展|第65屆柏林影展]]上首映<ref name="filmstage">{{cite web|title=Werner Herzog’s ‘Queen of the Desert,’ Jafar Panahi’s ‘Taxi,’ Anton Corbijn’s ‘Life,’ and More Will Premiere at Berlin 2015|url=http://thefilmstage.com/news/werner-herzogs-queen-of-the-desert-jafar-panahis-taxi-and-more-will-premiere-at-berlin-2015/|publisher=Filmstage|accessdate=2015-01-15|archive-date=2015-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115105505/http://thefilmstage.com/news/werner-herzogs-queen-of-the-desert-jafar-panahis-taxi-and-more-will-premiere-at-berlin-2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/programm/berlinale_programm/datenblatt.php?film_id=201510264#tab=filmStills |title=Life |accessdate=2015-01-28 |work=berlinale.de |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130175428/https://www.berlinale.de/en/programm/berlinale_programm/datenblatt.php?film_id=201510264#tab=filmStills |archivedate=2015-01-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2015年12月4日在美國戲院上映。

==劇情==
故事設定於1955年，敘述攝影師丹尼斯·史托克和好萊塢男星詹姆斯·狄恩在一場派對上首次碰面；狄恩想透過雜誌的照片來為自己添增名氣，因此瞞著老闆與丹尼斯一同到對方的家鄉[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]]，途中丹尼斯除了拍下他多張美照外，還為兩人產生了堅韌的友情<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson and Dane DeHaan Board James Dean-Based Film ‘Life’|url=http://screencrush.com/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-life/|publisher=Screen Crush|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2014-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212143048/http://screencrush.com/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-life/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson, Dane DeHaan To Star In James Dean Story 'Life' For Anton Corbijn|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-to-star-in-james-dean-story-life-for-anton-corbjin-20130905|publisher=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221221523/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-to-star-in-james-dean-story-life-for-anton-corbjin-20130905|archive-date=2014-02-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

